# Testing

## Web unit tests (Vitest)

- Location: `apps/web/src/**/__tests__/*.spec.ts` or colocated `*.spec.ts`
- Run: `cd apps/web && npm run test:unit -- --run`
- Mock `@/api/*` and Pinia stores; use `@vue/test-utils`

```typescript
vi.mock('@/api/taskApi')
const wrapper = mount(TaskCard, { props: { task } })
```

## API integration tests

- Project: `apps/api.tests/`
- `CustomWebApplicationFactory` — in-memory/test DB
- `AuthIntegrationTests` — login, register, protected routes

```bash
dotnet test apps/api.tests/Api.Tests.csproj
```

## E2E (Playwright)

- Package: `e2e/`
- `playwright.config.ts` starts api (`dotnet run --project apps/api`) + web (`npm run dev`)
- Tests: `e2e/tests/*.spec.ts`
- Run: `cd e2e && npm test`

## CI alignment

Match `.github/workflows/ci.yml` jobs: api → web → e2e (e2e needs both).
